[ Chuckles ]

43:29.566 --> 43:31.151
[Laughs]

43:31.276 --> 43:33.529
Sugar Plum...

43:33.654 --> 43:36.115
I promised you I would return,
and I have.

43:36.240 --> 43:38.075
And I've brought you
a new friend...

43:38.200 --> 43:40.911
-[ Car door opens]
-...to keep you company.

43:42.204 --> 43:45.833
Michael, this is my daughter,
Millie.

43:45.958 --> 43:47.626
Are you staying this time?

43:48.961 --> 43:51.004
Don't you have anything to say
to Michael?

